            <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 10:31:01 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>https://paste2ssh.com/changelog/</sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>
            <sparkle:version>6</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<style>
  :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
  .notes { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.55; padding: 2px; }
  .notes h2 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .notes ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
  .notes li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
</style>
<div class="notes">
  <h2>Version 1.2.0</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Uploads now go to <code>/tmp</code> on the server by default, which it clears on its own — so there's nothing to clean up.</li>
    <li>The automatic remote-deletion setting has been removed (no longer needed). You can still set a custom remote folder per host.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
]]></description>
